title: Over The Top- Ska Band
description:
Over The Top's First Ska CD Release + New Songs

Well, the tale of Over The Top is a long and complicated one. So I won't bother telling it. In short, they're from Sarnia/London, Ontario, they've been around for years, and play ska/punk/rock/motown/post-911-grunge-core.

Joe Iacobelli - Vocals and Bass
Nick Weed - Vocals and Guitar
Chris Reid - Drums and Percussion
Adam Stewardson - Trombone and Vocals
Lauren Korosec - Tenor Saxophone
Ryan Tang - Alto Saxophone
Alex Perdeaux - Baritone Saxophone
